Dar es Salaam. Former Young Africans Sports Club and National soccer team head coach Boniface Mkwasa has been appointed the club s secretary general.Young Africans Vice Chairman Clement Sanga introduced Mkwasa on Tuesday. Baraka Deusdedit had been acting in the position. Sanga said Baraka resumes his previous position as the team s financial director.Speaking during the press conference on Tuesday, Mr Mkwasa said he is happy with the appointment.